Package: twosfcaosrm
Title: Catchment-Based Two-Step Floating Accessibility with Local OSRM
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Original", "Implementation", role = "aut"),
    person("Maintainer", "Contact", email = "maintainer@example.com", role = c("cre", "ctb"))
  )
Description: Helpers to run 2SFCA accessibility models using isochrones or
    isodistances from a self-hosted Open Source Routing Machine (OSRM) instance,
    typically via Docker. Wraps batch isochrone queries, OSRM table requests for
    pairwise travel time or distance, supplier-to-demand spatial matching, and
    the classic 2SFCA supply-demand competition ratios.
